### Contact Me
You can reach me by email at nicolaschan99@gmail.com

### About Me
I'm a student in California. I like making interesting programs involving math and games. I've had experience creating web pages using html, css, javascript, and nodejs.

- [Web: JavaScript Functions](n-language/)
